3/07/descendents-milo-live-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/descendents-milo-live-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>主唱米洛·奥克曼（Milo Aukerman）遭遇“轻度心脏病”后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/descendents">后代</a>取消了欧洲巡演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/descendents-dave-grohl-nofx-fat-mike-9th-walnut-3006567">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ – 后裔</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支传奇的加州朋克乐队原定今年将进行一系列的演出，但为了让主唱休息和恢复，他们现在被取消了。</p><p> “我们真的很抱歉，但我们不得不取消即将举行的欧洲演出，”乐队在一份声明中告诉歌迷。</p><p> “我们的歌手米洛昨晚患有轻度心脏病。他状况良好，预计可以从手术中完全康复，但需要几周的时间才能恢复，然后我们才能再次上路。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvPjxRdx_iK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.4